org.forgerock.openam.cts.worker.CTSWorkerProcess

  • Packages that use CTSWorkerProcess 
    Package Description
    org.forgerock.openam.cts.worker
    Implementation classes that contain the CTS Reaper function, intended to clean up expired tokens in a multi-threaded fashion.
    org.forgerock.openam.cts.worker.process
    Package containing processes to be executed by CTSWorkers.

    • Uses of CTSWorkerProcess in org.forgerock.openam.cts.worker

      Constructors in org.forgerock.openam.cts.worker with parameters of type CTSWorkerProcess 
      Constructor and Description
      CTSWorkerTask(CTSWorkerQuery query, CTSWorkerProcess process, CTSWorkerFilter filter, String name)
      Worker task constructor, requiring a query which selects elements to be processed, a process defining the strategy for those elements, and a filter to remove elements to which the strategy should not be applied.
